## 6. Automatic License Conversion

### On May 1, 2028

If You have **not obtained a Commercial License** from the Licensor prior to the Change Date, Your rights under this License shall **automatically convert to the Apache License 2.0**, and the Licensed Work shall be made available under Apache License 2.0 at that time **without any additional action required**.

**Implications**:
- All previous versions remain under BUSL 1.1
- Versions released on/after May 1, 2028 are Apache 2.0
- You may continue using BUSL 1.1 versions; Apache 2.0 is optional upgrade path

